  m_text: 'Dear Daughter,

    Tomorrow, you will leave to study abroad.

    We
    are so proud of you.

    The happiness we shared in our family photo a few days
    ago is still fresh in our hearts.

    No matter where life takes you, this home
    will always be with you.

    Love,

    Mom & Dad'
